{{Path|/etc/portage/categories}} is a file that contains a simple list of valid categories that may be used in repositories and <code>PKGDIR</code>. The existence of a {{Path|categories}} allows for custom package categories to be created.

== Format ==

* One package category per line.

== Example ==

{{FileBox|filename=/etc/portage/categories|title=Categories file example|1=
app-hackers
media-other
}}
